name: Mitchell Little
description: With the curiosity of the features about to be shipped in the software, I tried to visualise the new features that I'd want to have. Driven by the same, I am focused on delivering the best user experience possible.

name: Tomas Prohaska
description: One of the most tragic things I know about human nature is that all of us tend to put off living. We are all dreaming of some magical rose garden over the horizon instead of enjoying the roses that are blooming outside our windows today.

name: Leon Funk Jr.
description: The best index to a person's character is (a) how hw treats people who can't do him any good, and (b) how he treats people who can't fight back.

name: Ms. Hope Beahan
description: You consider a man as educated only if he can pass exams. This education does not help people to equip themselves for the struggle of life.

name: Gerald Waters
description: Your time is limited, so don't waste it living someone else's life. Don't be trapped by dogma -which is living with the results of other people's thinking. Don't let the noise of others opinions drown out your own inner voice. And most important, have the courage to follow your heart and intuition.
